## 3️⃣ ROADMAP.md (Example)

```markdown
# CMFA Roadmap

This document outlines the planned milestones for the CMFA project.

| Stage | Description | Timeline |
|-------|-------------|---------|
| 0.1 | Concept validation, basic architecture definition | 2026 Q1 |
| 0.2 | Module prototypes, initial Fabric implementation | 2026 Q2–Q3 |
| 0.3 | Interoperability testing, standard documentation release | 2026 Q4 |
| 1.0 | Open standard release, community contributions and refinement | 2027 Q1 |

### Future Vision

- Expand module types and capabilities  
- Optimize Fabric for AI and HPC workloads  
- Establish open ecosystem for hardware manufacturers and developers

